sources.title: Gas House Kids Go West (1947)
sources.description: Carl Alfalfa Switzer, Tommy Butch Bond, Benny BartlettÂ

metadata.Plot: The Gas House Kids take a job delivering an automobile to California, unaware that it is a stolen car. Upon their arrival, they discover a hot-car ring run by a crooked ranch foreman with lecherous designs on the rancher's daughter.
metadata.Writer: Robert E. Kent, Robert A. McGowan, Eugene Conrad
metadata.Actors: Emory Parnell, Chili Williams, Vince Barnett
